data.description: Under Construction great new neighborhood in Mustang schools. This home will have Open living and an amazing stack rock fireplace. The Open Kitchen will have a huge work island, custom cabinets, beautiful granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry with an Awesome Barn Door. The Master bedroom will boosts a luxurious spa like ensuite with a huge walkin shower, closet with a built in chest and off season hanging. This home has many features normally found in more expensive homes. Easy access to the turnpike and interstate. Just minutes away from fine and casual dining, entertainment, shopping and healthcare. In the sought after Mustang Schools.  Photos of interior are from a similar home with the same floor plan. It shows some examples of similar features that will be put into this home - colors may vary.  Completion date to be the end of April.
